title: "HD - Garden of Blossoms"
date: 2024-12-29 12:00:00 -0000
author: HD
quote: "The blossoms open,"
subject: Haiku in the English-Speaking World (Early 20th century)
permalink: /Haiku in the English-Speaking World (Early 20th century)/HD/HD - Garden of Blossoms
---

The blossoms open,
a delicate unfolding,
a fresh breath of spring
inviting the world in,
while the sun hums,
a melody of warmth.
In this garden,
life is awakening,
a riot of colors, 
a burst of laughter,
where every petal tells
a story of hope,
a journey toward light,
a dance of becoming.


- HD
